            "url": "https://ttt.td/2023/02/17/free-images-hosting.html",
            "title": "分享自己使用LskyPro程序部署了一套图床",
            "date_published": "2023-02-16T19:15:07.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"嗯。。。\"><a href=\"#嗯。。。\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"嗯。。。\"></a>嗯。。。</h2><p><img src=\"https://input-s3.mn.input.im/adm-group/1/20230217/63ee82a746758.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"食用方法\"><a href=\"#食用方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"食用方法\"></a>食用方法</h2><p><strong>地址：</strong> <a href=\"https://input.im/\">https://input.im</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"概要\"><a href=\"#概要\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"概要\"></a>概要</h2><ul>\n<li>使用Lsky-Pro程序搭建</li>\n<li>使用了Cloudflare R2存储</li>\n<li>使用了Backblaze B2存储</li>\n<li>使用了GCore的CDN和OSS服务</li>\n<li>自建了一套MinIO存储</li>\n<li>利用闲置的机器自建了一套CDN服务(使用中)</li>\n<li>自建了NsfwJS的图片审核服务(上传可能会有点慢)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"使用条款\"><a href=\"#使用条款\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用条款\"></a>使用条款</h2><ul>\n<li>为避免滥用，游客身份有部分限制</li>\n<li>注册免费用户基本没有什么限制(一天传200张，差不多够了吧)</li>\n<li>严禁上传违法违规内容</li>\n</ul>\n",
            "tags": [
                "图床"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://ttt.td/2023/02/16/adguardhome-server-filter-china-domain.html",
            "url": "https://ttt.td/2023/02/16/adguardhome-server-filter-china-domain.html",
            "title": "使用AdGuardHome搭建私有DNS并对ChinaDomain进行分流",
            "date_published": "2023-02-16T07:15:27.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"先决条件\"><a href=\"#先决条件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"先决条件\"></a>先决条件</h2><p>编辑<code>AdGuardHome.yaml</code>设置<code>upstream_dns_file = &quot;/usr/share/adguardhome.upstream&quot;</code>，设置<code>all_servers = true</code>，设置<code>cache_optimistic = true</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"预览\"><a href=\"#预览\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"预览\"></a>预览</h2><p><img src=\"https://input-s3.mn.input.im/adm-group/1/20230216/63edd8a26bc44.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"分流规则\"><a href=\"#分流规则\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"分流规则\"></a>分流规则</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安装脚本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">curl -o <span class=\"string\">&quot;/usr/local/bin/upstream.sh&quot;</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BigUIFU/AGH_SELF/main/DNS/upsteam.sh&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">chmod</span> +x /usr/local/bin/upstream.sh</span><br><span class=\"line\">/usr/local/bin/upstream.sh</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 创建systemd服务定时更新</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">curl -o <span class=\"string\">&quot;/etc/systemd/system/upstream.service&quot;</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BigUIFU/AGH_SELF/main/DNS/upsteam.service&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">curl -o <span class=\"string\">&quot;/etc/systemd/system/upstream.timer&quot;</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BigUIFU/AGH_SELF/main/DNS/upsteam.timer&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl daemon-reload</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span> upstream.timer</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl start upstream.timer</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl status upstream</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n",
            "tags": [
                "DNS",
                "Linux"
            ]
        },
        {
